{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id77c2c2d9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460l–21"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"460l–21"},"text":"§ 460l–21.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definitions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"As used in this part:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77c2c2da-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460l–21/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “project” shall mean a project or any appropriate unit thereof.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77c2c2db-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460l–21/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “separable costs,” as applied to any project purpose, means the difference between the capital cost of the entire multiple-purpose project and the capital cost of the project with the purpose omitted.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77c2c2dc-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460l–21/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “joint costs” means the difference between the capital cost of the entire multiple-purpose project and the sum of the separable costs for all project purposes.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77c2c2dd-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460l–21/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “feasibility report” shall mean any report of the scope required by the Congress when formally considering authorization of the project of which the report treats.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77c2c2de-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460l–21/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “capital cost” includes interest during construction, wherever appropriate.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id77c2c2df-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/72/s10"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–72, § 10","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1965-07-09"},"text":"July 9, 1965","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/79/218"},"text":"79 Stat. 218","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id77c2c2e0-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id77c2c2e1-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id77c2c2e2-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This part, referred to in text, was in the original “this Act”, meaning ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/72"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–72","children":[],"tail":", which enacted sections 460"},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"l","children":[],"tail":"–12 to 460"},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"l","children":[],"tail":"–21 of this title and amended former section 460"},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"l","children":[],"tail":"–5(a) and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s662/d"},"text":"section 662(d) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
